Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
get_pba_mode(25.10)                                        get_pba_mode(25.10)

Name
       get_pba_mode  -  Displays  information  for the IPBA mode set using the
       set_pba_mode command

Syntax
       get_pba_mode

       [-help]

       [-quiet]

       [-nonDefault]

       Displays information for the IPBA mode set using the set_pba_mode  com-
       mand.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       -quiet Displays the current settings in Tcl list format only.

       -nonDefault
              Displays the current settings which are not default settings.

Related Information
              * set_pba_mode

              * report_timing

